      "content": "it just feels like you're reading from a manual. \"reach out,\" \"find a path,\" \"honor your life\"... it's all just noise. the reality is the noise is what's killing me. right now, the only thing that feels real is the emptiness. if i'm already at the bottom, everything is already broken. there's nothing left to lose, right? it feels like the only way to actually win is to just stop playing the game.",
